Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你不會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛犬飼隊長來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以槍支走火結案 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今晚閉店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天就開始工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那樣就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早點休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉色這麼差 可是不能去見客的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢 諷刺我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒欺負過你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是說你是好人嘛 是在誇獎你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.40,0:01:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喉嚨好乾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這具身體 應該沒有其他需求才對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.42,0:01:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是哪裡不舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不了麼
