Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚血的味道很濃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來你用什麼代價換取了她美麗的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種微不足道的女人 她的願望和我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:02.32,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:02.32,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:05.72,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:05.72,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:10.19,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:10.19,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:16.50,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾いた風に抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:16.50,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎面吹著乾燥的風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:22.97,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命への 真偽を覚え 刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:22.97,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂得了生命的真偽 銘刻於心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:26.38,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ただ 傍に居たいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:26.38,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 祈願待在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.95,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人を愛し 人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.95,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愛過 恨過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:32.45,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲しさは  優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:32.45,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲傷最後化作溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:37.42,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}例え光が 消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:37.42,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算陷入無盡黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:42.19,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:42.19,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍會尋覓明日希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:46.50,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃えた血の呼吸 消え寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:46.50,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃燒的血液 停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:51.57,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:51.57,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果之緣 最終轉化成奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:53.77,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:53.77,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.24,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.24,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:59.98,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闇を搔き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:59.98,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撥開黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:03.81,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手を伸ばすよ どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:03.81,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伸手向前 追尋你到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:06.08,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:06.08,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:09.72,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか 変えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:09.72,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總有一天 命運將會轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:14.39,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}涙の意味 無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:14.39,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要讓眼淚白流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:19.03,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}螺旋のように 蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:19.03,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如螺旋一般交織騷動的盡頭
